{
  "stem": "11641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I happened-- it was small potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I counted about 50 or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, for every potato, you get smacked on your behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was smacked on the behind for every potato.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it doesn't-- it didn't kill me, at least, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was almost the end of-- the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, at that time, Brunnlitz was-- comparing to everything else, it was sort of a heaven on earth in comparing to-- to others.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she was very instrumental.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Schindler should be mentioned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They arrived on the railroad track-- arrived a train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you heard voices inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You heard voices.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So Schindler-- she said, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let's open up and find out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the SS guy didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway, he was bribed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Open up, and you'll find over there human beings-- skeletons-- most of them frozen to death, some of them alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So open all the wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she, more or less, built a field hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those who were alived-- alive, she tried to nurse to life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Whoever died, died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Whoever-- a lot of them were alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Schindler bought a plot on a cemetery there-- some area-- I call it the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was-- they were buried proper way-- some of our-- our sort of quote, unquote inmates-- over there from this area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They're called [NON-ENGLISH] at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And a lot of them were alive, and everything because of-- of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Not that he was such a good husband, but as far as she was a-- and she's still alive, by the way, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But she was instrumental in-- in saving many lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- if they-- if they died, it was natural death.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
